{"title":"Windows_Reverse1","slug":"Windows_Reverse1 WP","date":"2021-01-17T14:02:36.210Z","updated":"2021-01-17T14:28:09.124Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Windows_Reverse1 WP.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":null,"covers":["https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210117215443379.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center","https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210117215938470.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center"],"content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=reverse&number=4&grade=1&id=5514&page=2\">Windows_Reverse1</a></p>\n<ol>\n<li>检测是否有壳<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210117215443379.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></li>\n</ol>\n<p>发现有upx壳，于是使用upx -d进行脱壳，并对脱壳后的程序使用ida分析</p>\n<p>2.观察main函数后，发现经过sub_40100（）函数后，得到了字符串DDCTF{reverseME}，<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210117215938470.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>3.sub401000后发现，分析为对字符串查询为在ox402ff8后的地址，将其作为字典取出，注意前后存在的多余空格字节，就可以得到flag：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>ZZ[JX#,9(9,+9QY!</p>\n</blockquote>\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}